  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Green beans, also known as string beans or snap beans, are slender, elongated
    vegetables that grow on flowering plants in warm climates. They are typically
    bright green, though some varieties may appear yellow or purple, and are harvested
    while still young and tender, before the seeds inside fully develop. Green beans
    have a crisp texture and a mild, slightly grassy flavor that becomes softer and
    more savory when cooked. They are a good source of vitamins such as vitamin C,
    vitamin K, and folate, as well as fiber, which supports digestive health. Green
    beans are commonly prepared by steaming, saut\xE9ing, roasting, or boiling, and
    are often used in salads, casseroles, and side dishes."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
